 # #  ---  if, else, elif, and nested if
            # here we enter to the logical thinking part of the python code
            # if is akeyword in python which is known as suite where we can write multiple stements 
            to make it logicaly . it helps us to decision making either true or false.
            # under the if statement what ever we put the logic or statement it will be exicuted and gives us the out put.
            #to make the code logically stong and without repiting the if statement again again we use the else statement
            # the else statement is used to perform the operation when the if statement is false.
            # the elif statement is used to perform the operation when the if statement is false and it is under the if statement.
            #indentation is required for the exicution of the if ,else , elif statements so inplace of using space we use the tab botton for the proper estimation of the indentation.
            # nested if statements mean that a if statement in side a if statement like a nest so proper indation is required for the exicution of the statements.

 # #  ---  Loop
      --- While loop
            # Loop is used to generate a number of statements in the loop that will be executed in the  current iteration   of  the loop .
            # while loop is used to generate a number of statements where we don't no the how much time we want to execute the statements.
                e.g when generating a password etc.
            # for using loop we need three things thai is
            1. initialization
            2. condition
            3. increment/decrement
            # while loop is used to execute the statements in the loop until the condition is true .
            # when the condition is false while loop exit.
            #  that means while loop is used to execute the statements in the loop until the condition is false .
            # We can use a while loop inside a while loop to generate a number of statements, which is called nested while loop.
            # in nested while loop first initialization of the outer loop is start then the inner loop is run untils the inner loop is facing a condition which is false then the inner loop is exit. after tha the outer loop is exicuted then the process is repeted like this untill the the outer loop condition is not false .

 # #  --- For loop
            # Normaly for loop is used or work with the sequence like tuple, set, dictionary, string  and array where we know about the sepecific range of the sequence.
            # for loop is used to execute the statements in the loop for a specific number of times.
            # for using for loop we need three things such as starting point, ending point and increment/decrement.
            # we can use the range concept in for loop.

 # #   --- Break, Continue, pass.
            # Break, Continue, pass these re mostly the keywords that are used in the loop for a specific number of times for run the program accodring to the user interest.
            # Break is used to exit the loop when the condition is true. it will not executed the remaining part of the loop.
            # Continue is used to continue the loop when the condition is true and it will executed the remaining part but left the true part of the loop.
            # Pass is used to skip the current iteration of the loop and it will come out of the loop.
            # we can use the break, continue, pass keywords in the for loop and while loop.
            # we can use the break, continue, pass keywords in the nested loop.
            
            
            


            
            

            

                

            
                      


            



            



            
           
           
           
             
  